name: Hold on
description:
I am falling, 
but I never hit the ground.
I am flying,
but I never felt free.
I am like a bird strangled to a string. 
A string tied loosely in my hand.
I try hard to let go of the string, 
But I still hold on to it.
Even on the verge of wearing out.

| Rendered on 8 November 2021
| 2668 × 4002 [JPEG]
